This repo includes the dissertation PDF. Ensure you have the right to redistribute the PDF in this repository and to publish it as a dataset DOI record.
See `metadata/RIGHTS.md` for notes and where to update the license if needed.

## How to cite

Once you mint a DOI, cite the dataset DOI (preferred). Until then, cite the repository:

> Goldston, J. L. (2019). *Critical Success Factors in Enterprise Resource Planning Implementation in U.S. Manufacturing* [Dataset]. GitHub repository: https://github.com/<YOUR-ORG>/erp-csfs-delphi-us-manufacturing-2019.

(Once you have a DOI, `CITATION.cff` will generate accurate citations automatically.)
